# Assignment 4: Transmission Failure Demonstration

## 📌 Course Details
- Course: Computer Networks (ENCS304)
- Program: B.Tech CSE
- Experiment: Link Errors & Retransmission

---

## 🎯 Objective
To demonstrate how communication is affected when a network link fails and how it recovers after reconnection.

---

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Cisco Packet Tracer

---

## 🧪 Network Setup
- Devices Used:
  - 2 PCs (PC0, PC1)
  - 1 Switch
- IP Configuration:
  - PC0: 192.168.40.1 /24
  - PC1: 192.168.40.2 /24

---

## ⚙️ Steps Performed

### 1. Setup
- Connected both PCs to the switch using copper straight-through cables
- Assigned IP addresses to both PCs

